      "sanskrit": "etadeva prapañcayati – vihāyeti| kāmān viṣayān nispṛhatayā vihāya yaścarati – bhakṣayati| bhakṣayāmītyādyahaṅkāra mamakāravarjitaśca| sa hi pumān| sa eva muktimadhigacchatītyarthaḥ",
